<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="inner fade">
    <span class="sec-label">Our Promise</span>
    <h1 class="hero-title" style="font-size:clamp(40px,7vw,72px);margin-bottom:18px">Climate Commitment</h1>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:var(--w55);max-width:540px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.65">Tureko holds itself to the highest environmental, social, and governance standards — because a sustainable future demands accountability.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="section" style="padding-top:20px;padding-bottom:120px">
  <div class="inner">

    <!-- BADGE BANNER -->
    <!-- BADGE IMAGE PLACEHOLDER -->
    <div class="badge-banner fade" style="margin-bottom:36px">
      <div class="badge-circle">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/>
          <path d="M15.477 12.89L17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,38px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.04em;margin-bottom:12px">Tureko Sustainability Certified</h2>
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--w55);max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.72">Every Tureko-partnered business earns the right to display our Digital Sustainability Badge — a verified mark of genuine climate commitment.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="commit-grid">

      <!-- ENVIRONMENTAL POLICY -->
      <div class="gc fade">
        <div class="c-icon-box">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6 2 2 8 2 14c0 4.4 3.6 8 8 8 1.4 0 2.8-.4 4-1 4-2 6-6.4 6-10C20 5.6 16.4 2 12 2z"/><path d="M2 14c4-2 8-2 12 0"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="c-title">Environmental Policy</div>
        <ul class="policy-ul" style="margin-top:18px">
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Measure and disclose carbon emissions across all operations annually.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Achieve net-zero carbon footprint in all Tureko-managed projects by 2030.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Eliminate single-use plastics from all partner operations by 2026.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Source all operational energy from renewable sources where feasible.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Implement a zero-waste policy in all internal and client-facing activities.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- CLIMATE STANDARDS -->
      <div class="gc fade d2">
        <div class="c-icon-box">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14 14.76V3.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0-5 0v11.26a4.5 4.5 0 1 0 5 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="c-title">Climate Standards</div>
        <ul class="policy-ul" style="margin-top:18px">
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Aligned with the Paris Agreement 1.5°C warming limit pathway.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Compliant with DENR Environmental Impact Assessment requirements.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Following GRI Standards for environmental reporting and disclosure.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Adopting TCFD recommendations for climate-related financial disclosures.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Conducting annual third-party climate risk assessments for all projects.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- SUSTAINABLE TOURISM PRINCIPLES -->
      <div class="gc fade d1">
        <div class="c-icon-box">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"/><line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="c-title">Sustainable Tourism Principles</div>
        <ul class="policy-ul" style="margin-top:18px">
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Respect and protect the natural and cultural heritage of all destinations.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Maximize economic benefits for local communities and businesses.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Minimize physical, social, behavioral, and psychological impacts of tourism.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Support biodiversity conservation and ecosystem restoration efforts.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Promote environmental education for tourists, staff, and operators.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- ESG COMMITMENT -->
      <div class="gc fade d2">
        <div class="c-icon-box">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="c-title">ESG Commitment</div>
        <ul class="policy-ul" style="margin-top:18px">
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span><strong style="color:var(--white)">Environmental:</strong> Reduce Scope 1, 2, and 3 emissions across all engagements by 40% by 2027.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span><strong style="color:var(--white)">Social:</strong> Prioritize fair wages, safe working conditions, and community benefit-sharing.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span><strong style="color:var(--white)">Governance:</strong> Maintain full transparency in reporting, ethics, and anti-corruption practices.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Integrate ESG metrics into every client contract and quarterly review.</li>
          <li><span class="p-dot"></span>Publish an annual Sustainability Impact Report available to all stakeholders.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- ACCOUNTABILITY STATEMENT -->
    <div class="gc fade" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(34,197,94,0.07),rgba(20,184,166,0.07));border-color:rgba(34,197,94,0.18)">
      <div style="max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;padding:16px 0">
        <div class="c-icon-box" style="margin:0 auto 22px;width:56px;height:56px">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size:24px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.035em;margin-bottom:16px">Statement of Accountability</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--w55);line-height:1.82">Tureko holds itself fully accountable to the commitments outlined on this page. We believe transparency is the foundation of genuine sustainability. We welcome scrutiny, engage in open dialogue with partners and communities, and continuously raise the bar for responsible tourism practice. If we fall short of any commitment, we will disclose it promptly and take corrective action — no exceptions.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:32px">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Partner With Tureko</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
